  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TheNighfall</h2>Victoria moves with her family to a new city to start her new job. But the first <br>night in her new house is completely different than expected.<br>As her husband and their two children are coming a day later she has to stay <br>the first night alone in their new house. <br>What starts with insomnia and a slight malaise first becomes an absolute <br>nightmare during the night.<br><br>Will you be able to survive this night until dawn?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Atmospheric horror experience of a special kind<br></li><li> Thrilling story-line<br></li><li> Breathtaking soundscape<br></li><li> Realistic and detailed graphics<br></li><li> Interactive surrounding<br></li><li> Original music by Northpolyptica</li></ul>",
